headline: IFF Unveils China Scent Exploration Program to Drive Next-Generation Fragrance
summary: IFF (NYSE: IFF) today launched its China Scent Exploration Program, a comprehensive consumer learning initiative designed to create fragrances specifically for the Chinese region. This program builds on IFF's deep regional expertise, which began in 1981 when it became the first multinational fragrance company to establish operations in China.
